dcMetadata.abstract_tsi: Finished, colored, topographical map showing Mount Hope Bay, Bristol Peninsula, the mouth of the Warren River, and the northern part of the island of Rhode Island.; Details of a British amphibious operation to Bristol and Warren are shown on the map with symbols of military units, figures of naval vessels, and notations.
